        <item>
            <title>騰訊 AI「混元-T1」正面迎戰 DeepSeek，效能跑分聲稱全面對打 GPT-4.5 與 o1</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/hunyuan-t1/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hunyuan-t1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/hunyuan-t1/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
