        <item>
            <title>Grok vs Google Gemini，AI 改圖大比拼</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/grok-vs-google-gemini/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=grok-vs-google-gemini</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/grok-vs-google-gemini/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 11:59:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Gemini]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Grok]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299142</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前小編和大家分享過 Google Gemini 2.0 的改圖功能（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/google-gemini-ai-2/ai/">相關教學</a>），最近 Grok 也推出了類似功能，輸入簡單文字可以替你修改圖片。現在就讓小編和大家實測一下，到底哪個 AI 改圖功能更加強勁。</p><p>以下小編就叫 Grok 和 Gemini 幫小嫻戴上太陽眼鏡：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299241" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/52544350120_115c18b0-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/52544350120_115c18b0-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/52544350120_115c18b0.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原圖</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299240" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image15-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image15-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image15.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Grok 生成的圖片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299239" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-6-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-6-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-6.jpeg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Gemini 生成的圖片</p><p>現時在香港使用 Grok 無須 VPN，但如果要試玩 Google Gemini 的話就需要先開啟 VPN。</p><p>Grok 網址：<a href="https://x.com/i/grok">https://x.com/i/grok</a></p><p>Google Gemini 2.0 網址：<a href="https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/">https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/</a></p><h2>實測 1：更改衣服顏色</h2><p>小編上傳了一張沙律的照片，分別要求 Grok 和 Google Gemini 2.0 將襯衫改為藍色，看看哪個 AI 生成的結果更好。小編使用的指令為：把襯衫改為藍色</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/54022952068_230e5de3-386x580.jpeg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/54022952068_230e5de3-386x580.jpeg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/54022952068_230e5de3.jpeg 599w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原圖為白色襯衫</p><p>小編首先測試 Grok 的 Edit Image 功能，選擇「Edit Image」後，上傳小嫻的照片並使用「把背心改為紅色」指令。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445442-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445442-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445442.jpg 885w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299166" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450216-484x580.jpg" alt="" width="484" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450216-484x580.jpg 484w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450216.jpg 751w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 484px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Grok 一次會生成 2 個版本供你選擇</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299167" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image5-1-386x580.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image5-1-386x580.jpg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image5-1.jpg 599w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲效果算是自然</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299168" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image6-1-386x580.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image6-1-386x580.jpg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image6-1.jpg 599w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 但面部卻被不明原因修改</p><p>之後小編使用同一照片同一指令，測試 Google Gemini 2.0 的修改圖片功能。小編留意到，Google Gemini 2.0 生成速度較 Grok 為慢，而且一次僅可生成一張圖片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445547-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445547-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032445547.jpg 746w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450049-469x580.jpg" alt="" width="469" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450049-469x580.jpg 469w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032450049.jpg 727w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299165" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-2-385x580.jpeg" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-2-385x580.jpeg 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-2.jpeg 598w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲衣服顏色有點奇怪，生成得不太自然</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032464238-620x580.jpg" alt="" width="620" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032464238-620x580.jpg 620w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032464238.jpg 651w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 620px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲顏色過度非常不自然</p><h2>實測 2：更改背景</h2><p>接下來小編上傳了一張沙律的相片，分別要求 Grok 和 Google Gemini 2.0 將背景改為沙灘。小編使用的指令為：將背景改為沙灘</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dscf0731-387x580.jpeg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dscf0731-387x580.jpeg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dscf0731-scaled.jpeg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原圖</p><p>要求 Grok 更改背景後，Grok 生成的圖片的確是沙灘，但就更改了沙律的姿勢，而且額外為沙律增加了一條絲巾。除此之外亦更改了沙律的樣子，完全認不出她。另外放大看的話，可見腳趾非常不自然。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更改了原本的姿勢</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-1-694x281.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="281" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-1-694x281.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image4-1.jpg 1249w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲放大看可見腳趾細節不自然</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image3-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image3-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image3.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲額外增加了一條絲巾</p><p>與 Grok 相比，Gemini 就可忠實還原沙律本人，但就沒有考慮到光暗過渡等問題，感覺像是直接「退地」然後把沙律貼在沙灘上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299169" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-3-385x580.jpeg" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-3-385x580.jpeg 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/generatedimagemarch2-3.jpeg 598w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲欠缺光暗處理，失卻層次感</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
